=== CREATION_MYTH_MURAL ===
# id: 69
# title: The Creation Myth
# chinese_title: 创世壁画
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A vast mural depicts a creation myth rendered in a blend of alien and human artistic styles. In the beginning, there was a single stroke. From that stroke, all radicals emerged, and from radicals, all meaning. The universe itself was written into being.

* [Study the mural's depiction of primordial radicals]
  ~ gain_radical("大")
  "创" (chuàng) — to create, beginning
* [Photograph each panel systematically]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "画" (huà) — painting, to draw
* [Search for hidden symbols in the artwork]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "藏" (cáng) — hidden, to hide
